Description




Havelock Europa PLC is an interior solutions provider. The Company operates in the retail, lifestyle, corporate services and public sectors. Its sectors also include financial services, education, accommodation and leisure. Its services include interior design, equipment design and manufacture, supply and installation, procurement and project management. Its range of in-house capability spans architectural services, interior design, product design, space planning and graphic design. The equipment it produces, imports and buys in, is brought together and palletized through its kitting operation. Its United Kingdom network provides management contracting that complements its design, furniture manufacture and installation service. Its capability ranges from minor works to building strip out, heating, ventilation, and air conditioning installation and refurbishment. Its customers include retailers, commercial and financial organizations, construction companies and education authorities.
  More from Reuters » 







